# LAB-OP systems context (token-aware index)

## When to apply this rule

Any prompt that mentions: solar / growatt / inversor / painel solar / energia gerada /
enel / fatura / consumo / conta de luz / UDM / UniFi / VLAN / rede / WiFi /
HVAC / ar condicionado / LG / Springer / BTU / R-22 / R-410A /
T14 / latitude / <lab-host-2> / pi3b / Attiv / UPS / homelab / lab-op /
hardware inventory / coleta de dados / relatorio de energia.

## 1. Required private-file read chain

Read in this order -- stop when you have enough context for the task:

1. `docs/private/homelab/OPERATOR_RETEACH.md` (B1-B6) -- hardware facts, HVAC plates, VLANs, solar IDs, burst host
2. `docs/private/homelab/OPERATOR_SYSTEM_MAP.md` -- topology, accessibility matrix, software versions
3. System-specific file per section 2 below

